howtoinvestfordummies.model

Class InvestmentStrategiesModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • howtoinvestfordummies.model.InvestmentStrategiesModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InvestmentStrategies
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    StockInvestmentStrategiesModel

    public class InvestmentStrategiesModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements InvestmentStrategies
    Provides an implementation for common activities related to all the type of investments. This includes creating Portfolios, examining its content, getting all the portfolios, and checking portfolio value and cost at certain period.
